text: Andre Tucker is an American football Trainer and currently the Head Athletic Trainer for the NFL's Chicago Bears. He was previously Assistant Head Athletic Trainer for the Miami Dolphins, the Jacksonville Jaguars, the Atlanta Falcons and the Cleveland Browns. ==References== Category:Living people Category:American strength and conditioning coaches Category:Chicago Bears coaches Category:Cleveland Browns coaches Category:Atlanta Falcons coaches Category:Jacksonville Jaguars coaches Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
